Subject: Re: [T2] Gear to cam bolt torque?

Tom, That sounds acceptable.

As long as you have .040 at the pump, you are OK..You can clearance the
studs a bit if they are too close for you..

This is an important step, one that alot of guys miss..
Jake Raby
Raby's Aircooled Technology
http://www.aircooledtechnology.com
